[[sn:Yin Earth Ox]] [[ja:己丑]] [[zh:己丑]] [[ko:기축]] [[fr:Buffle de terre]] [[de:Erde-Büffel]] [[en:Yin Earth Ox]] [[af:Aardeos (astrologie)]] [[de:Erde-Büffelen]] [[en:Earth Ox]] [[fr:Buffle de terreboishak]] [[it:Ki-chṳ́id]] [[sn:ichinja]] [[vi:Kỷ Sửu]] [[za:Keiceij]] [[ar:Yin Earth Ox]]
<!--please transliterate all the hiragana readings into romaji and provide the kanji-->

{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Earth Ox|kanji=己丑|romaji=tsuchinoto ushi|onyomi=kichū|p=jǐchǒu|w=chi-ch'ou|mi=t͡ɕi³⁵ ʈʂʰoʊ̯|y=gei2 chau2|j=gei2 chau2|ci=kei tsʰɐu̯|mc=kɨj tʂʰjuw|oc-bs=kɯʔ ʈʂʰuʔ}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}} '''Yin Earth Ox also known as Jichou''' (己丑) is one of the [[Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|Chinese sexagenary cycle signs]].
It is the 26th combination of the [[Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|Sexagenary cycle comprehensive]], preceded by {{ill|Wuzi (戊子)|ja|戊子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Gengyin (庚寅)|ja|庚寅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. According to [[Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory]] theory, the [[Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stem]] {{ill|Ji (己)|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yin [[earth]], while the [[Earthly Branches|Earthly Branch]] {{ill|Chou (丑)|ja|丑|1=Ox (zodiac)|lt=Ox (丑)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} also represents yin [[earth]], making this a [[Five Elements|harmonious combination]].
== Years of Jichou == A year is Jichou if the remainder when divided by 60 is 29. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of Jichou''' |- ! [[1st millennium]] !! [[2nd millennium]] !! [[3rd millennium]] |- | * 29 * 89 * 149 * 209 * 269 * 329 * 389 * 449 * 509 * 569 * 629 * 689 * 749 * 809 * 869 * 929 * 989 | * 1049 * 1109 * 1169 * 1229 * 1289 * 1349 * 1409 * 1469 * 1529 * 1589 * 1649 * 1709 * 1769 * 1829 * 1889 * 1949 | * 2009 * 2069 * 2129 * 2189 * 2249 * 2309 * 2369 * 2429 * 2489 * 2549 * 2609 * 2669 * 2729 * 2789 * 2849 * 2909 * 2969 |}
== Jichou Months == In years ending in 0 or 5 (when the Heavenly Stem is {{ill|Geng (庚)|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Yi (乙)|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}), the twelfth lunar month is a Jichou month. This is determined based on the [[Chinese lunisolar calendar]], meaning it may also be calculated using the [[solar term]] system (from [[Lesser Cold]] to the day before [[Beginning of Spring]]).
== Jichou Days == A Jichou day follows a 60-day cycle.
=== Special Characteristics === Jichou days are the 6th day in the [[Ten Days of Mourning|Ten Days of Mourning]] (十方暮). == See Also == * {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Chinese calendar|ja|中国暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}
