== Jichou Months == In years ending in 0 or 5 (when the Heavenly Stem is {{ill|Geng (庚)|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Geng (庚)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (庚)|qq=}} or {{ill|Yi (乙)|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|lt=Kinoto (乙)|2=ja|3=乙|4=zh|5=乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yi (乙)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (乙)|qq=}}), the twelfth lunar month is a Jichou month. This is determined based on the [[Chinese lunisolar calendar]], meaning it may also be calculated using the [[solar term]] system (from [[Lesser Cold]] to the day before [[Beginning of Spring]]).
